Package de.uni_koeln.spinfo.strings.plugin.algo.lca

Interface Summary
TreeNode This interface is used to pass a tree to the LCA algorithm.
 

Class Summary
CycleDetector This is a cycle detector based on Exercise 7 of section 3.1 of Volume 2 of Knuth's "The Art of Computer Programming".
JunitLCA Test harness using the Junit test framework for LCA.
LCA The Lowest Common Ancestor algorithm of Schieber and Vishkin (sequential version only), roughly as described in "On finding lowest common ancestors: simplification and parallelization", by Baruch Schieber and Uzi Vishkin, SIAM J.
Log2 container for static methods, such as log base 2
Swatch Simple 'StopWatch' class to accumulate timing info
TestLCA Test LCA.
